{"tid":1770884,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"安俊英PRODUCE1-4季作幣行動","createTime":"2019-12-05T12:28:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T15:04:16.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"61b2e09908c02309bcb850f5b80696c4533f9f50","tid":1770884,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T12:28:16.000Z","msg":"用大白話整理一下安俊英等人的罪行。<br />\n<br />\n第一季：第一輪選拔時淘汰了兩個原本不該淘汰的練習生，換了另外兩個上來。<br />\n<br />\n第二季1：第一輪淘汰時調換了兩個練習生的排名（一個60名內，一個60名外）<br />\n第二季2：最終回直播時調換了兩個練習生的排名。讓排在前11位的C某淘汰，排在後11位的D某出道。<br />\n<br />\n第三季：為了排除自己不想要的練習生，在最終回前選定出道成員和排名。<br />\n<br />\n第四季1：改動了5月的觀眾網絡投票和現場投票，在第一輪選拔時淘汰了一個原本不該淘汰的練習生，換了另一個上來。<br />\n第四季2：在第三輪選拔時淘汰了兩個原本不該淘汰的練習生，換了另外兩個上來。<br />\n第四季3：為了排除有出道經歷的練習生，在最終回前選定出道成員和排名。<br />\n<br />\n接受4家公司5名管理層共計47次招待，幫助（旗下藝人）出演第三季第四季，並進行有利的剪輯。"},{"pid":"e03b5d4e77a535c32335532a4b57ff49dcbf7e3f","tid":1770884,"uid":208486,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T12:28:52.000Z","msg":"幤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee1a8226578c7a4bc6947fced427e07ecf9a9461","tid":1770884,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T12:30:08.000Z","msg":"好想知真實排名係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad8d82ed12d62437bb159a64821bb25c25ab706","tid":1770884,"uid":229026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T12:32:13.000Z","msg":"我要殺死安俊英呢個仆街！<br />\nI must kill this fucking ajy!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qD8rB6L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqD8rB6L.jpg&h=52d70f79&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb45412235b71363d10f1136f2cbbadb846724ad","tid":1770884,"u